column5: Thats a 1000 posts. Taken me about 4.5 yrs, and I dont think there's one about my    prowess.At my age I dont need to 'boast'. been there, done that. Thanks to all, for an interesting 4.5 yrs.
Thank you for being a part of this wonderful world Jack!!!
Uummm....I still have quite some typing to do to reach 1000 but working on it.  Congrats Jack Leechman
Congrads! I will be there one day
And everyone a worthwhile read...  Congrats my friend...
Wholeheartedly agree with Norm, Jack. It`s not the quantity of posts(I should talk,   )its the quality. Yours definately were. Congrats.
Yes, ditto... thanks for being part of our community!
Well done and very much looking forward to the next 1,000!!  Was a pleasure seeing you again and meeting Jackie this past weekend.  Look forward to seeing future pictures of "Teddy"
Congrats on the milestone Jack, hope the summer is treating you well!!!!  Cheers, 1leg
Congrats!!! and hope u would stay and give us another 1000!
Congrats.. Opps one more post for me
Good stuff Jack! Definitely quality posts.
